    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a mechanically sound example of BMW's high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system, both of which have been meticulously serviced to ensure peak volumetric efficiency across the powerband. Power is routed through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock, providing exceptional traction. Critical preventative measures have been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing inspection. The chassis dynamics remain tight, benefiting from refreshed suspension geometry and bushings. While the exterior shows honest patina from spirited use, the drivetrain and structural integrity are optimized for the discerning driver who prioritizes performance and analog feedback.",
